"ICE SHEET"

Category: ^gMANIPULATION^n
Duration: ^gPERMANENT^n

Ice Sheet covers the ground of the local area in a sheet of ice
for a short period of time. The duration of the spell is determined
by the force and once permanent cannot be dispelled or destroyed
until it naturally melts.

It causes difficulty in movement both in and out of combat.

Vehicles attempting to drive in an area covered by Ice Sheet are
force to make crash tests, possibly damaging or destroying the
vehicle.


^WSee Also: CAST^n
